{"tid":715153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[毒藥是真的] 廣東普寧幼兒園兩童疑「毒鼠強」中毒　一人死亡","createTime":"2018-06-24T09:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T09:09:55.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b556f40869f11d9d597c783c4062416e709961d2","tid":715153,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1403347-20180624.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1403347-20180624.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=bckJ5nBkCG1TFIvHuFK0OiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f1d2018a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1403347-20180624.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5b41c2a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1403347-20180624.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n廣東普寧市一間幼兒園一名學童中毒死亡，初步檢測懷疑「毒鼠強」中毒，另外一名學童情況穩定，無生命危險；當局已扣查幼兒園負責人。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，事發在上星期五，出事的幼兒園位於麒麟鎮月嶼村，當局昨日收到報告指，兩名學童出現抽搐和嘔吐等症狀，送院搶救，其中一名學童搶救無效死亡。幼兒園其他學童未發現異常情況，當局成立特別領導小組，調查和處理事件。"},{"pid":"bf02c15076cd09f6ff6a65f6a19ebbfe9262dd14","tid":715153,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T09:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}